text: BREAKING: From Sunday to Sunday, Florida reported 59,036 new coronavirus cases, the highest amount in a one-week period since the pandemic began. The state has now seen over 200,000 positive infections, according to the health department. https://t.co/axva9gBj24 https://t.co/s00BIHsmaB
